## Abstract
**Introduction:** [Brief context of the condition and its importance]
**Case Presentation:** [Summary of the patient and key findings]
**Intervention/Treatment:** [Management approach provided]
**Outcome:** [Results and follow-up]
**Conclusion:** [Key learning points and implications]

**Keywords:** [3-5 keywords separated by commas]

## Introduction
- Background of the condition/disease
- Epidemiology and prevalence
- Current understanding of pathophysiology
- Importance of reporting this particular case
- Unique aspects or educational value
- Brief literature context

